   SOFIA Telescope Components - Get details on the components of the
   telescope.
   go to SPIE papers Airborne Astronomy Papers - A collection of 46 papers
   on the SOFIA first-light instruments, the SOFIA telescope design,
   observatory systems and closely related topics.


